      "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "TO: Director, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "DATE: August 20, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "FROM: SAC, Springfield",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISC",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Reference is made to Bureau Bulletin No. 42, Series 1947, dated July 30, 1947 re the above.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "For the Bureau's information a Mrs. [REDACTED] of Saybrook, Illinois reported to this office the finding of a flying disc in her front yard at 6:00 A.M. on July 26, 1947.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "It appears from investigation conducted by an Agent of this office that the stability of [REDACTED] is questionable. However the alleged flying disc was obtained and it is apparently the concoction of some of the juveniles in the area. It is an old wooden platter, which has assembled on it a silver plate, a spark plug, a timer, and some old brass tubing. Photographs were taken of the same and there are six views enclosed herewith.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "No doubt this was someone's idea of a prank.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "The disc is presently being retained by the Springfield Office and will be retained pending receipt of Bureau advice relative to its' destruction. The thought in retaining it was that perhaps the Bureau might desire to have it transmitted to Washington for any novel value it might have.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
